name: NEWFOUNDLAND PLANE SPOTTING! St. John's International Airport (YYT)
description:
St. John's is Canada's easternmost city and the capital of the province of Newfoundland and Labrador.

As such, it's home to Atlantic Canadian carrier PAL Airlines, and receives plenty of traffic from other Canadian operators throughout the day.

I spent a couple hours spotting there back in July following the conclusion of the Dash-8s-across-Canada trip and captured some of YYT's regulars!
